    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Welcome to Gunnies – where explosive action meets absolute chaos in a zany third-person shooter like no other!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/43ed812389ad379f0fbf254a61e01268.poster.avif?t=1748434406\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/43ed812389ad379f0fbf254a61e01268.webm?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/43ed812389ad379f0fbf254a61e01268.mp4?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Gunnies</i>, it’s all about the thrill of PvP combat. Choose your team and jump into intense, fast-paced deathmatches where every second counts. Fight your way to victory by outmaneuvering enemy players, outsmarting traps, and mastering unique weapons that bring explosive results. With chaotic, ever-evolving arenas and unpredictable hazards, <i>Gunnies</i> keeps you on your toes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/ff5c5bbe3034d7e50ea908126a769dc6.poster.avif?t=1748434406\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/ff5c5bbe3034d7e50ea908126a769dc6.webm?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/ff5c5bbe3034d7e50ea908126a769dc6.mp4?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Face the Zombunny Horde</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While your main target is the opposing team, the <i>Zombunnies</i> won’t make it easy! These relentless, zombified bunnies spawn throughout the map, adding an extra layer of challenge. Work with your team to fend off waves of these bouncy foes, but stay sharp – they’re just as dangerous as the players you’re fighting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/fe93399e394d3465f884aacbaf476090.poster.avif?t=1748434406\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/fe93399e394d3465f884aacbaf476090.webm?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/fe93399e394d3465f884aacbaf476090.mp4?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill Cards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock unique perks like custom multi-kill voice announcements, visible health bars, and extra visual effects, gaining a tactical edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/727bdd9ecc68b494ca8a1b12c3fab606.poster.avif?t=1748434406\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/727bdd9ecc68b494ca8a1b12c3fab606.webm?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/727bdd9ecc68b494ca8a1b12c3fab606.mp4?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Weapons for Unique Playstyles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a range of quirky weapons, each with unique effects to suit your playstyle. Go stealthy, go loud, or go explosive – every weapon adds a new twist to the action and can turn the tide in your favor when used strategically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/e9d9543a9123fb631fe05e632db27e58.poster.avif?t=1748434406\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/e9d9543a9123fb631fe05e632db27e58.webm?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/e9d9543a9123fb631fe05e632db27e58.mp4?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lootboxes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get in-game rewards such as cosmetics, accessories, skill cards &amp; weapon skins</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/a84a61f36d4c68fe8392ce16cadf061c.poster.avif?t=1748434406\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/a84a61f36d4c68fe8392ce16cadf061c.webm?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323030/extras/a84a61f36d4c68fe8392ce16cadf061c.mp4?t=1748434406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PvP-Focused Action</strong>: Experience the thrill of player-vs-player combat with up to X players per match.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zombunny Challenge</strong>: Face waves of Zombunnies that add a new layer of tension to every encounter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Maps</strong>: Navigate hazard-filled maps with traps and random events that keep the gameplay fresh.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Weapons</strong>: Wield an array of crazy weapons, each with its own hilarious and deadly effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team Play</strong>: Work together or go solo – strategize with your team or forge your own path to victory.</p></li></ul>",
